snippet.title: JoeyHighStakesTV: Al-Kanan Industries | Scythe Dev Team
snippet.description:
Join JoeyHighStakesTV as he starts up a new Vlog series. In his first Vlog stream, Joey will be wandering the abandoned Al-Kanan Industries. Al-Kanan is infamous for being a shady organization, their activities shrouded in secrecy. One of their factories just outside of Northbury Grove, deep within Specter Forest, suffered a terrible chemical spill. There were no survivors. After this terrible tragedy, Al-Kanan disappeared entirely from Sabit - all of their locations, abandoned and left to rot. 

Years later, another tragedy struck - several bodies were found within the ruins of the long abandoned Al-Kanan Industries. 

And now, Joey is gonna investigate the building, over a decade since the chemical spill and just a YEAR after the Northbury Grove Massacre. What will he find?

Find out on itchio!
https://scythedevteam.itch.io/entity

Joey played by Dillon Burris 
Status-Post theme by Kyle Brauch
